{"type":null,"faqId":22240,"title":"怎么优化 Wi-Fi？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.1.21.2.1.1.1\"></a><span>如果 Wi-Fi 信号比较弱，可以尝试调整一下荣耀路由的位置。选择开阔空间，减少荣耀路由和上网设备之间的阻挡物，例如水泥墙、木板墙等阻挡物会影响 Wi-Fi 的无线信号传输效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.1.21.2.1.2.1\"></a><span>如果  Wi-Fi 的速率较低，可以尝试连接到荣耀路由的5G Wi-Fi。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.1.21.2.1.3.1\"></a><span>如果搜索附近有多个 Wi-Fi，可以尝试更换一个信道，以避免干绕。更换信道方法：登录荣耀路由 Web 配置界面，进入“</span><span class=\"s2\">更多功能 &gt; Wi-Fi 设置 &gt; Wi-Fi 高级</span><span>”页面，在“</span><span class=\"s2\">2.4G Wi-Fi 信道</span><span>”和“</span><span class=\"s2\">5G Wi-Fi 信道</span><span>”中更换。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.1.21.2.1.4.1\"></a><span>如果房子太大导致有些地方 Wi-Fi 信号弱，可以将两台荣耀路由级联，实现整套房子的 Wi-Fi 全覆盖。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6121","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428566145000,"seriesProductName":"WS831-10","visitedTimes":246,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WS831,荣耀路由","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}